Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:42.15,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\be1\pos(607,280)}『夏 日 慶 典』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們來到的是這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄高中麻將部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的「閃亮社團少女」採訪的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻將部一年級生  原村和同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊…真是可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哪…哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:03.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}其實原村同學是去年中學生全國大賽的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  咲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:06.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}實力可是很強的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小京
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日慶典？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.63,0:03:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這週
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期末考試也剛剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是正好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去邀請麻將部的大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  咲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有浴衣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是難得的節日  就穿來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…可以倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來咲邀請來小和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能與和一起過夏日慶典了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就這樣  讓小和和咲一起穿上浴衣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得熱嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你在看哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說「看哪裡」嘛  那當然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:03:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有節日祭典啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞…搞什麼嘛  突然冒出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節日祭典的話就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用浴衣下面不經意露出的性感內衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有人迷得神魂顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又說出跟自己相差甚遠的詞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希  說起來  有什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了說了  大新聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從部長那裡聽來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又要準備去集訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來…原村同學也說過參加全國大賽之前要再去集訓一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像定在下週末了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且聽部長說似乎還請了重要的嘉賓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要嘉賓？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…要請來天才帥哥美容師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能讓小咲跟我也有小和那樣奢侈的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說誰的胸部奢侈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學  採訪結束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人氣角色也很麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  優希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是說好了從現在開始要一起學習的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣  小咲  京太郎  在活動室等你們囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…等等！優希！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由清澄高中麻將部發起的四校集體集訓的邀請…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我們鶴賀的三年級生就要引退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想要找比賽對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個月全國比賽就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在與全國比賽中的魑魅魍魎們比賽之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要盡可能地和強手比賽的心情我可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.06,0:06:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縣預選決賽的對手之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風越和龍門渕至少也算是全國級別的隊伍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說我們算是贈品嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄可沒有惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說其實也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的部員也能和全國級別的選手進行練習了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哈哈  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻將部好不容易走到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:32.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我和你畢業了  也想讓它能繼續走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就回覆她們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  我也想去久違了的社團裡露一下臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經游得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海裡也能游了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哈哈  小桃你也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和清澄一起集體集訓？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要擊敗瞭解全國大賽的實力的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進一步提高自己的實力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們可是沒什麼好處
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好處可大著呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的原村和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縣預選時沒有分出勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我真正的偶像對決
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要痛快地分個勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對局進行中起立是違反規則的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說不是已經分出勝負了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之  透華的意思是贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村禾想和衣一起玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  還能和清澄的嶺上使一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣的玩伴好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟衣講道理也行不通的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  意向如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去參加集訓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:07:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我知道了  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和  全帶幺九  寶牌2  8000點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不及格？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說期末考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  優希之前完全沒有進行考試準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果數學沒能及格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  本週五下午要進行補考
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週五就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是夏日慶典那天嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.68,0:08:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！既然是夏日慶典的話  補考就請假好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且補考再不及格的話就要參加補習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能去集訓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希  我也來幫忙  一起來為補考複習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲  小和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天就先來打麻將  明天再開始學習好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始就要學習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打麻將
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把這個寄出去吧  萩義
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  透華大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…感謝貴部之前的集訓邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們非常樂意接受…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.41,0:09:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…用不著讓我來寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  睦月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是下一任的部長  只能讓你來寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如學姐說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小睦學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加…加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.70,0:09:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…好吧  我會盡我所能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:09:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  隊長呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天已經先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說清澄發起的集體集訓邀請了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長回覆了沒有啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…還沒決定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長去參加全國比賽之前能和強手比賽絕對是好事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是隊長不想只為了自己的練習去參加集體集訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們…不能和她一起去全國大賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:00.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}閃亮社團少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天我們來到的是這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}清澄高中麻將部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天的「閃亮社團少女」採訪的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}麻將部一年級生  原村和同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那…那個…大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊…真是可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:20.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}其實原村同學是去年中學生全國大賽的冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  優希在週五有補考？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果補考不及格的話  從下週開始要參加補習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣搞不好我們的部員會缺席集訓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…小和與咲一定會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.79,0:11:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風越還沒有回信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…幫優希想想辦法好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:11:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動室禁止使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本週全天  一年級生禁止使用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還打算讓小和她們一起在活動室幫我學習的說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本週全天？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希的補考
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  到週五的補考結束為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法  回家算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:22.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣…去圖書室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:33.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  要在這裡學習的話  放她們進來也未嘗不可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在活動室裡的話  優希肯定會說想打麻將的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊  但是連其他的一年級生也禁止也有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這三個人從進入麻將部到縣預選為止  已經打得夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下週的集訓開始後  到全國大賽又將會天天麻將的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少現在這段時間讓她們忘了麻將吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  說起來一年級生好像不止三個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實集訓需要的物資有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是魔鬼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後參照這邊  畫在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎  優希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.54,0:13:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.83,0:13:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡好像有點不合適的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  明天換個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:34.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（墨西哥餅專賣）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥餅兩份  讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  學習呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我全吃完…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:47.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把墨西哥餅全部吃掉後再開始學習！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快點吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加的雞肉墨西哥餅五個  讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥餅真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這裡也不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:04.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（墨西哥餅裡好暖和）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書館？和學校的圖書室不一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城鎮的中央圖書館有自習室的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能隔音  學習的話還是沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那麼帶上墨西哥餅出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全濕掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道這樣的話就不必跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和還是那麼怕閃電啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來我剛進社團的時候  好像雷也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你還是追上來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點忘我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總…總之先進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.81,0:15:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人都沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為下雨的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說期末考試一般也都結束了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了補考而來圖書館學習的大概也只有我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是什麼值得高興的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨還沒有停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要下到晚上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷陣雨而已  不會下那麼長時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下雨天待在房間裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時感覺好像世界就只有那麼大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這時候外面都是海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這房間就是漂浮在海上的小船之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候也會這麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮永同學還真是文學少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…只是   不知不覺這麼想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥餅…墨西哥餅…全濕掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是墨西哥餅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墨西哥餅變成這樣就沒法戰鬥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的學習到此結束啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.08,0:16:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會放過你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會長  這是暑假時期的活動計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補考  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:16:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…有找會長您的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤焦了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優希
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補考怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之都寫上去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這看來要確定去補習了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  該做的也都做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  補考也結束了  大家去參加夏日慶典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補考的成績還不知道呢  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  原村同學不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我可沒有說我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！慶典的墨西哥餅店舖  全部制霸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有墨西哥餅店舖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！要說慶典的話就是墨西哥餅啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算參加集訓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  回覆晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必特地過來的說  打個電話就可以了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是學生會長呢  還兼任麻將部的部長  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們麻將部總共也才六個人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和名門風越的隊長不能比的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是個不合格的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次集訓的事也沒辦法一個人決定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  學妹們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.23,0:18:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加集體集訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們希望隊長能活躍在全國的舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得為了明年做準備  必須參加集訓增強實力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊…隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很懂事的學妹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這也都是好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很好嗎  大家都有這麼好的學妹們陪伴著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來你有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.19,0:19:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然輸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了墨西哥餅店舖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然真的有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  過於吵鬧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.30,0:20:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望集訓點能有賣墨西哥餅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花可不是流星喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了個大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:07.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（成功囉！）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  開始集訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:10.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わたしもしたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ココロは正直　ドキツモ快感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.28,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手加減しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四角い宇宙で　テンパイすちゃらか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:24.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,テンパイ即リー快感すちゃらか　青春当然ハコテンぶっとび
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:30.38,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}クイタンあとづけ連チャンサクサク　ハイパイいーしゃん天国らりほー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:35.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当たって（誰でもこいな）　狙って（何でもこいな）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:38.11,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和了りはどんでん返し（リーツモウラウラごめーん）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:44.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いけないわ　ホンキだして（半チャンもういっちょ！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:47.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,読みって（オカルトないし）　打ちって（味方いないし）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:49.18,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流れはもってかなくちゃ（追っかけリーチいゃーん）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:54.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}足りないわトキメキ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:23:00.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼くような面子がどうしたの？（トイトイトイトイ）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:03.73,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わたしとしようよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:06.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ココロが晴天　ドキツモ昇天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:09.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手加減しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.39,0:23:12.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四角い宇宙で　テンパイらりるれ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:17.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,テンパイ即リー快感すちゃらか　しーさんしーさんしーさんぷたぷた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:23.31,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦燥先ヅモかんちゃんずっぼし　満場感動焼き鳥泣き泣き
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:26.05,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,スカートひらりと（タメンチャンなら）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:28.85,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキドキツモ（ウキウキです）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.92,0:23:31.59,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髪の毛さらりと（ドラアンコで）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:34.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ズキズキツモツモ（しあわせです）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:10.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想來喲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中確實心跳不已　自摸快感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.28,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要手下留情喲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.35,0:22:19.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在四方的宇宙裡聽牌唰啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.16,0:22:24.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽牌就立直快感唰啦啦　青春自然要戰到負分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.71,0:22:30.38,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}吃斷後付接著是連莊　配牌一向聽天國來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:35.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中（來吧誰都行）　瞄準（來吧什麼都行）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:38.11,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和牌逆轉（立直自摸兩張裏寶牌對不起了）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:44.20,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了呢　拿出真本事（再來一局半莊{\redj}！{\r}）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.27,0:22:47.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀牌（沒有超自然）　出擊（沒有自己人）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:49.18,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運勢不抓住可不行（緊接著立直　不要啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.21,0:22:54.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}心跳還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:23:00.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我隱隱作痛的面子去哪了{\redj}？{\r}（碰碰和碰碰和）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:03.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我來戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.80,0:23:06.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中是晴天　自摸升天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:09.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要手下留情喲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.39,0:23:12.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在四方的宇宙裡聽牌啦哩嚕咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.17,0:23:17.67,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽牌就立直快感唰啦啦　十三十三十三不搭不搭
